    <field id="description" text-type="text/html"><![CDATA[In many cases you will receive a specification in form of an excel document. In this case you will need to extract all relevant test cases out of the document and manage them as separate test cases.<br/>
 
<ul>
  <li>Go to <span style="font-style: italic;">Work Items|Operations|Import|Format: Microsoft Excel Workbook<br/>
      </span></li>
  <ul>
    <li>Choose Import File provided to you or found on <a href="/polarion/#/project/MyPolarion/home" target="_blank" class="descriptionLink"><span id="WIKI_LINK:_default.Home|Home"></span> </a><br/>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <li><span style="font-style: italic;">Import as new document named &quot;Test Specification</span>&quot; in space &quot;Specification&quot;<br/>
    <img src="attachment:import1.png" style="width: 724px;height: 150px;"/><br/>
    </li>
  <li>Apply following settings<img src="attachment:excelimporter2.png" style="width: 724px;height: 207px;"/><br/>
    
